divs: Sighting DetailsHey my names Oscar. About a week ago whenever that meteor shower was going on, me and my friend were laying down on a soccer field looking at the sky trying to see the meteors and all that. Then we saw a weird square looking thing. The weird thing about it was that I dont remember any lights on it (but my friend claims that it had a orange light) but I could still clearly see it. It was flying in a choppy zig zag path. Really weird... It did like 3 zig zags with a pause in between each one, and then shot off extremely fast. Just vanished. The crazy thing was the next morning in my biology lab I overheard a girl a couple tables down talking about seeing a weird thing flying in the sky, I immediately jumped in and said I saw it too. Weirdest thing I have ever seen. Have you heard any other stories like this?
